as we've discussed.

03:43.040 --> 03:44.610
I understand, Ms. Lauler...

03:44.680 --> 03:45.966
And I do not want bushy hedges.

03:46.040 --> 03:47.690
You do not want
bushy hedges. (SIGHS)

03:47.760 --> 03:49.091
We talked about this.

03:49.160 --> 03:51.367
