Many times.

03:51.560 --> 03:53.085
All right, I'll trim
the bushes myself.

03:53.160 --> 03:54.207
Give it to me.

03:54.280 --> 03:55.770
Yes.
Thank you.

03:55.880 --> 03:57.166
And you can cut the grass.

03:57.600 --> 04:01.571
You cut the grass yesterday.
In a diamond pattern.

04:02.720 --> 04:03.881
Yes.

04:05.160 --> 04:06.764
Then I guess you can go.

04:07.320 --> 04:08.685
Thank you.

04:10.280 --> 04:12.089
Oh! These are not sharp.

04:12.880 --> 04:15.121
Look, Louis, you have
to have these sharp.

04:15.240 --> 04:17.447
I'll look in the truck. Please.

04:18.160 --> 04:19.844
